column2: SELECT nsaid, ra, dec, z, elpetro_absmag_g as g, elpetro_absmag_r as r, elpetro_th5#_g as g_radius, elpetro_th5#_r as r_radius, elpetro_mets as Metallicity, elpetro_mass as Mass, (#*z/#) as Dist, (elpetro_absmag_g+.#* (elpetro_absmag_g-elpetro_absmag_r) ) as AbsMag, (elpetro_absmag_g+.#* (elpetro_absmag_g-elpetro_absmag_r) # +#*log (#*#*z/#, #) ) as AppMag, (.#* (elpetro_absmag_g-elpetro_absmag_r) +.#) as Color FROM nsatlas WHERE (#*#*z/#) > #
